Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs) :
1. What hair colouring services does CodeHair offer for women?

At CodeHair, we offer a comprehensive range of hair colouring services for women, including highlights, balayage, ombre, root touch-ups, full colour, and more. Our expert stylists are skilled in various techniques and will work with you to achieve the perfect hair colour that complements your skin tone and enhances your features.

2. How do I know which hair colour is right for me?

Choosing the right hair colour can be overwhelming, but our experienced stylists are here to help. During your consultation, we'll take into account factors such as your skin tone, eye colour, lifestyle, and personal preferences to recommend the perfect hair colour for women. We'll also provide expert advice on maintenance and upkeep to ensure your colour stays vibrant and beautiful.

3. How long does a typical hair colouring appointment at CodeHair take?

The duration of a hair colouring appointment at CodeHair can vary depending on the complexity of the service and the length and thickness of your hair. On average, a standard hair colouring appointment can take anywhere from 1.5 to 3 hours. During your consultation, your stylist will provide you with a more accurate estimate based on your specific needs and desired outcome.
